      "name": "Spiral Strangling",
      "description": "Silvanna thrusts her lance in the target direction and spins it 6 times while gaining a 350( +150% Total Magic Power) shield. Each spin deals 165( +45% Total Magic Power) (Magic Damage) and slightly pulls targets toward the center. Silvanna spins 1 additional time for every 50% of extra Attack Speed she possesses. The skill deals only 50% damage against Minions. (Spiral Strangling) counts as a Basic Attack but cannot Crit.",
