      "description": "Silvanna leaps to the target location and creates a Circle of Light upon landing, dealing 350( +110% Total Magic Power) (Magic Damage) to enemies in the area, slowing them by 40% for 1.5s, and restraining the closest enemy hero to the area for 3.5s. (This skill cannot be interrupted.) Silvanna gains 100% Attack Speed and 40% Lifesteal when in the Circle.",
